  "body": "In community channel, when I am mentioned -> there is:\r\n\r\n1. notification badge with counter for the community (left pane )\r\n2. blue dot for the exact channel where this unread message is\r\n3. counter increase in activity center\r\n\r\nHowever , when i open that particular message, the counter at the Community badge and Activity center are not decreased (the message is not considered as read). \r\n\r\nWhen i send one more message in this chat, the counter at community badge decreases (message is read) but activity center is still showing unread.\r\n\r\n<img width=\"1552\" alt=\"Screenshot 2021-09-15 at 10 44 22\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/82375995/133392623-3497b0d9-18fa-4ff7-b6f8-d6313d56a664.png\">\r\n\r\nExpected: when the message is read (i did navigate to it by clicking PN or scrolling) - the counters should reflect accordingly\r\n",
